      <akn:section eId="sec_29_304_41">
        <akn:num>29-304.41</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Corporationâ€™s acquisition of its own shares.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_29-304_41_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>A corporation may acquire its own shares and shares so acquired shall constitute authorized but unissued shares.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_29-304_41_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>If the articles of incorporation prohibit the reissue of the acquired shares, the number of authorized shares shall be reduced by the number of shares acquired.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
